{"tid":1247512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉：政府應派員與示威者對話","createTime":"2019-06-21T06:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T08:39:38.000Z","uid":212626,"like":708,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"651e9f59d5c3608f700c6684e3bdd0757025a611","tid":1247512,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:31:45.000Z","msg":"聯及多間大專院校學生會，不滿政府未有回應反修訂《逃犯條例》示威者的訴求，將行動升級，發動今日包圍政府總部。示威者到11時前佔據添美道，並將多個水馬及雜物搬出，夏慤道的東西行車線目前都有車輛被阻塞，無法行車。<br />\n<br />\n身兼行政會議成員的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀表示，已向行政長官林鄭月娥建議，政府派員與示威者對話。她指出，政府暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》，實質與撤回草案無異，大家不用再斟酌字眼，而目前集會已影響了政府和立法會運作，對市民構成不便，希望政府能考慮她的建議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRcsgTo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRcsgTo.jpg&h=87249712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource：信報"},{"pid":"ebc92e1728c38804c938525e8c0129d3907899e0","tid":1247512,"uid":11934,"like":570,"dislike":0,"score":570,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"就派你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d17bc704397132e1c9358b6a47000de2148478d","tid":1247512,"uid":48083,"like":199,"dislike":2,"score":197,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:33:50.000Z","msg":"又補刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317b3068c3f5af7568bc4cfacd1a28a5106a0b06","tid":1247512,"uid":88167,"like":300,"dislike":0,"score":300,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"不用斟酌字眼？你朋友元秋唔撚係咁講喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a696e3f1bccc7ed892c3e831dd5a86cb0288c5ba","tid":1247512,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14f39258cf0632c081df358dd2de44274d4975d","tid":1247512,"uid":41963,"like":115,"dislike":1,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"